{"product_id":"reise-leave-in-conditioner-50ml","title":"REISE Leave-In Conditioner 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePlant-sourced moisturizing ingredients, organic plant extract relieving sensitive discomfort, improve dry skin problems.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe plant oil repair formula is absorbed quickly into the hair without leaving a sticky feeling. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIt allows easy combing and leaves the hair light and refresh.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eRice Amino acid moisturizing formula increases hair moisture content. Liquid gold Argan Oil, Rice Bran and Camellia Oil repair damaged, fuzzy and split hairs, moisturizing hair and improve dryness restoring glow. Added vitamin B5 helps strengthen the hair and increase elasticity. Reproduces bright, smooth and elegant hair. Can be used on both wet and dry hair without rinsing out, suitable for all hair types. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCaprylhydroxamic Acid preservative, alcohol-free, and contains no animal derived or stimulating ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eAfter washing your hair, dry any excess water out and pour appropriate amount of hair oil to the palm of your hand. Apply evenly to damp hair for your hair to absorb, then dry your hair. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStore in cool, dry place away from direct sunlight.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eArgania Spinosa Kernel Oil, Rice Bran Oil*, Rice Amino Acids, Camella Oleifera Seed Oil, Sea Salt Extract, Cetearyl Olivate, Citric Acid, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Sodium Anisate, Citrus Aurantium Dulcis Oil, Cymbopogon Flexuosus Oil(Cymbopogon Citratus\/Cymbopogon Citratus Leaf Oil, Panthenol, Tocopherol.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Ingredients from certified organic agriculture\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAnimal ingredients free | Silicone-free | Alcohol-free | Fragrance-free | No Parabens preservatives\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMade In Taiwan\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Reise","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49274438910279,"sku":null,"price":27.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/reise-leave-in-conditioner-50ml-937676.jpg?v=1739897350","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/reise-leave-in-conditioner-50ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}